articles.title: Romanian nationalist and Trump ally Simion wins first round of presidential vote - CNN
articles.description: Eurosceptic George Simion won the first round of Romania’s presidential election re-run on Sunday, partial results showed, after a ballot seen as a test of the rise of Donald Trump-style nationalism in the European Union.
